==用途==
邻氯甲苯和对氯甲苯可以作为[[氯化苄|氯化苄]]、[[苯甲醛|苯甲醛]]和[[苯甲酰氯|苯甲酰氯]]合成的前体。<ref>{{Ullmann|doi=10.1002/14356007.o06_o03|title=Chlorinated Benzenes and Other Nucleus-Chlorinated Aromatic Hydrocarbons|year=2011|last1=Beck|first1=Uwe|last2=Löser|first2=Eckhard|isbn=978-3527306732}}</ref>

